{"missionId":"9220bdaf-396a-48d2-bfa5-eb0290711235","eventType":"MESSAGE_SENT","sourceAgent":"wf-9220bdaf39-manager-4-quality","targetAgent":"wf-9220bdaf39-worker-4-1-quality-reviewer","eventData":{"senderId":"wf-9220bdaf39-manager-4-quality","receiverId":"wf-9220bdaf39-worker-4-1-quality-reviewer","messageId":"187","messageContent":"审查本周用户增长相关各部门行动方案的质量：逐项检查是否包含明确目标、目标用户/场景、关键动作、负责人、时间节点、资源需求、成功指标、数据口径与验证方式；识别逻辑跳跃、证据不足、指标不一致、执行路径不清和缺失项。输出按部门的审查清单：1) 已满足项，2) 主要缺口，3) 必须修订项，4) 建议补充证据或示例。","messageType":"INSTRUCTION","status":"SENT"},"metadata":{"phase":"planning","stageKey":"planning"},"eventId":"c6cedcb5-7499-43b0-9171-63c247112220","timestamp":1775299864192}
